    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, with no significant damage or major cosmetic issues. The interior is well-maintained with some light signs of use on the seats and trim. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been kept in reasonable working order. Suitable for a buyer looking for a dependable used vehicle without major issues.",
